s/a3a0a392-9978-4e81-b8e8-4ea44ca1d2d0.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7 5p Progress Report — AHV Works] You are the 5-minute change-detecting reporter for the AHV Works ecosystem.\n\nCheck sessions_list. Compare current active sessions against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 9:38 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 09:38 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776159540409,"__openclaw":{"id":"f4d11278","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the sessions list and compare against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ea7ytn8jnyb_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"messageLimit":2}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2ea7ytn8jnyb_2","name":"memory_get","arguments":{"path":"heartbeat-state.json","corpus":"memory"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":438,"output":94,"totalTokens":14476,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":0,"cost"