n completing naturally (already reported at 08:38). Pipeline stable.\nSystem: \nSystem: **Silent exit.**\nSystem: [2026-04-14 09:13:11 UTC] The heartbeat-state.json is empty (memory retrieval returned no data). Comparing against the prior 5p report (08:38 UTC — reported by cron:e7885813), the 3 monitoring crons are still running with no new failures, no new blockers, no new sessions spawned. Pipeline is stable.\nSystem: \nSystem: **Silent exit.**\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 9:14 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 09:14 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776158090281,"__openclaw":{"id":"31a1b178","seq":88}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"HEARTBEAT_OK - all crons stable, no changes to report."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1464,"output":25,"totalTokens":48072,"cacheRead":7778,"cacheWrite":38805,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776158090589,"responseId":"062d388b31ef64253d42eb2515bc2717","__openclaw":{"id":"493a9778","seq":89}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ac986a8d-2425-40c7-835b-ed9b101b0bff","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Send this exact message to Telegram group -5163901258:","displayName":"Cron: Send this exact message to Telegram group -5163901258:","updatedAt":1776156272410,"sessionId":"d6d5ae17-2a68-46a3-beb9-a2a98cf2f1b5","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":15116,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"running","startedAt":1776156271891,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestra